</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ronney Jenkins 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Hueneme 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Football 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Junior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: Jenkins, promoted to the varsity as a sophomore, began 
this season with the respect of all Channel League coaches. He gained 494 yards 
in 75 carries last season, and he already has surpassed that total in three 
games this year, gaining 519 yards in 63 carries.Jenkins has been a key for 
Hueneme's resurgence. The Vikings won only twice in the past five seasons but 
have won twice in three games this year. 
</P>
<P>
