</P>
<P>
 In the news: Comedy writer Tony Peyser, on L.A. Marathon organizers admitting 
the laundering of $73,000 in campaign contributions to local and state elected 
officials: "To them, 10K isn't a race; it's the cost of a city council member." 
</P>
