reelection campaign: "He's challenged his opponent to tour the state for a 
series of debates, and said, 'I'll drive.' " 
</P>
<P>
 Comic Argus Hamilton, on the President's physical exam: "The doctor ordered 
him to get more rest. Clinton has trouble sleeping at the White House, so 
they're flying in Ronald Reagan to show him how." 
</P>
